collections.name: It's so me
collections.description:
Whilst creating my collection of art works, I came to an arrival and realisation, that I  was -creating me! My favourite saying is, ‘when good things fall apart, greater things fall together!’ 
So come connect with me through my art, through the femme, abstract, pop art, avant-garde, which embodies my creations, my love, my humour, the world of colour that I love and all that I create, sending out it to you and the universe, to love, laugh and enjoy – it’s so me! And I’m just getting started with creating!!!!

collections.name: d7 susi man
collections.description: “Susi Man” (すし男) is a character born long ago in Sapporo, Japan. One day, when planning to go out for sushi with his coworkers, he inexplicably decided to visit Hands (a popular store) to buy costume items, then secluded himself in the restroom to transform into Susi Man. Still in costume, he proceeded with his coworkers onto the subway and headed straight to the sushi restaurant.

collections.name: AI Brushstrokes
collections.description:
“AI Brushstrokes” is a unique digital art collection that merges the power of artificial intelligence with the beauty of abstract expression. Each piece in this collection is created using advanced AI techniques to simulate the spontaneity and depth of traditional brushstrokes, resulting in visually stunning artworks that blend digital precision with an organic touch.

This collection is a harmonious fusion of color, texture, and light, where AI takes on the role of the artist to redefine modern digital art. Whether you are a collector seeking exclusive pieces or an enthusiast of creative technology, AI Brushstrokes offers an unparalleled visual experience that inspires imagination and pushes the boundaries of NFT art.

🔹 Rarity: Each piece is unique and one-of-a-kind.
🔹 Style: Abstract digital brushstrokes.
🔹 Technology: AI-generated with artistic refinements.
🔹 Join us on this journey into the future of art!

collections.name: Fragments of a Digital Mind
collections.description:
Fragments of a Digital Mind is an avant-garde NFT collection exploring the intersection of AI, human creativity, and surreal abstraction. Each artwork is a dreamlike fragment of an AI’s evolving consciousness, blending AI-generated compositions with hand-drawn surrealist details.

This collection envisions how AI perceives reality, depicting floating cities, cosmic minds, synthetic muses, and floral codes entwined with digital patterns. Every piece is a glimpse into machine intelligence awakening to creativity, where precision meets imagination.

With limited editions and unique storytelling, Fragments of a Digital Mind is more than an NFT series—it’s a philosophical reflection on AI as an artist. Own a piece of a digital dreamscape and step into the future of AI-generated creativity.
